= $13,380 - $5,400
= $7,980

Next, we need to determine how many months it will take for Mr. Dubois to fully pay off the remaining amount by paying $420 each month. We do this by dividing the remaining amount by the monthly payment.

Number of months = Amount still to be paid / Monthly payment
= $7,980 / $420
= 19

Therefore, the car will be fully paid for in 19 months.

